{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Play a note, and a chord is generated, per the requested root, scale & intervals.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Scales are defined as Reaper scale .txt files, and should be in the ix_scales folder. This script assumes one scale per file.\par}
}

